For example, studies on the effects of the 4th dose are already rolling in from Israel.
And according to these studies, in most patients there is a fivefold increase in antibodies, which already has the long-term effect you mentioned.
Just like any other vaccine, it will have its own vaccination schedule in time, but it's too early for that now.
Another fact is that a new vaccine based on an inactivated virus is expected to hit the market soon, which, according to the manufacturer's specifications, promises up to 10 times greater effectiveness.
